- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possibility as the paper discusses the size of semigroups, which is related to information theory.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is a possibility as the paper involves proving a bound on the size of syntactic semigroups, which can be seen as a logical problem.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possibility as the paper deals with the complexity of languages and automata.
